---
import SiteLayout from '../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro'
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Dinosaur Treasure Hunts for Kids | ThinkMystery"
  description="Printable dinosaur treasure hunts for kids with clues, hidden fossils, explorer adventures, and indoor rainy-day fun."
  is_staging={false}
>
  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="hero-simple">
      <p class="eyebrow">Dinosaur Treasure Hunts</p>

      <h1>Dinosaur Treasure Hunts for Kids</h1>

      <p class="lede">
        Dinosaur treasure hunts combine clue-solving, exploration, and hidden surprises into a
        screen-free adventure kids instantly understand. They work especially well for dinosaur-themed
        birthdays, rainy days, and indoor weekends.
      </p>

      <a class="button primary" href="/scavenger-hunts/dinosaur/">
        Browse dinosaur scavenger hunts
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="content-card">
      <h2>Why dinosaur themes work so well</h2>

      <p>
        Dinosaur activities naturally create excitement because kids already understand the world:
        fossils, explorers, hidden eggs, treasure maps, lost creatures, and secret discoveries.
      </p>

      <p>
        A good dinosaur treasure hunt taps into that curiosity while giving kids something active
        and interactive to do instead of simply watching a screen.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-card">
      <h2>Best uses for dinosaur treasure hunts</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Dinosaur birthday parties</li>
        <li>Rainy-day indoor activities</li>
        <li>Classroom reward games</li>
        <li>Weekend family activities</li>
        <li>Playdates and sleepovers</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="content-card">
      <h2>Looking for dinosaur scavenger hunts?</h2>

      <p>
        Our dinosaur scavenger hunts are already live and are a great fit for younger kids who
        love clue trails, searching games, and treasure-style adventures.
      </p>

      <a class="button secondary" href="/scavenger-hunts/dinosaur/">
        Explore dinosaur scavenger hunts
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
